633
00:35:10,840 --> 00:35:12,800
I did a lot

634
00:35:12,880 --> 00:35:14,160
to raise Fu Zifang on my own.

635
00:35:15,080 --> 00:35:17,680
Someone's jealous
and wants to steal

636
00:35:17,920 --> 00:35:19,360
