for touching your precious body

661
00:37:16,640 --> 00:37:17,760
without your permission?

662
00:37:19,960 --> 00:37:20,720
It's not like that.

663
00:37:21,920 --> 00:37:23,000
I have nothing to lose.

664
00:37:27,040 --> 00:37:28,320
