691
00:38:59,760 --> 00:39:00,880
Unreasonable.

692
00:39:02,000 --> 00:39:03,000
Immoral.

693
00:39:03,480 --> 00:39:04,600
Unfaithful.

694
00:39:05,200 --> 00:39:06,400
Irresponsible.

695
00:39:08,960 --> 00:39:12,800
All you men are no good.

696
00:39:32,560 --> 00:39:33,400
I assume

697
00:39:34,040 --> 00:39:35,680
