698
00:39:39,680 --> 00:39:41,000
Does it make you feel better
after saying that out loud?

699
00:39:54,080 --> 00:39:54,880
Thank you.

700
00:39:58,160 --> 00:39:58,880
I'm sorry.

701
00:40:01,520 --> 00:40:03,120
We're both hurt.

702
00:40:03,640 --> 00:40:04,640
