722
00:41:26,600 --> 00:41:27,480
Did you get married?

723
00:41:28,640 --> 00:41:30,040
Do you have a girlfriend?

724
00:41:32,240 --> 00:41:33,320
How can you talk so much

725
00:41:33,800 --> 00:41:35,120
